_sText: Description: 	This is a remake of the classic Counter-Strike map, cs_bloodstrike. This version includes barrels, fog and cool lighting. Early on, I saw the cs_bloodstrike_s map, but it looked like it had been put together in five seconds, with textures done poorly and all sorts. So I decided to try and do a better version of it. I hope you like it. Also included is a nav file for the bots.
